 was furious about the book.  Always ostentatious}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid11867278 , }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid11867278\charrsid13904672 
