ing cultural concepts of kinshi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid9330635 p behaviour: his book very short}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid13904672\charrsid13904672 
, making some of the students who did the interviews furious.  Material never written up in detail, but the files are in the Special Collections.  Schneider used analogy with language to understand kinship concepts.  Meanwhile also George Robe}{
