, demographer, had concluded that statistics did not capture enough on kinship, and had begun looking at interviewers' comments in the margins.  So }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid8336828 Raymond}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
