d up.  Did these in Kingston and in Jamaican rural villages.  Donald Rowbotham (in the centre of the island), Michael Fisher (in the east), and Nancy Foner (on the north coast) all did locating survey interviews.  Funded by }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 
