\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid13904672\charrsid13904672 With David Schneider collaborated, and then disagreed.  Schneider focussed on culture but not on the social system.  He became darling of ge
nder and gay rights anthropology.  After he retired, went to Santa Cruz; died recently.  Cantankerous person, always fighting with people.
